sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist / Client
    participant Envoy as Envoy Proxy
    participant AIGateway as AI Gateway<br/>ExtProc 9004/gRPC
    participant GWExt as GW API Inference Ext<br/>EPP 9002/gRPC + BBR 9004/gRPC
    participant KServe as KServe
    participant CaikitTGIS as Caikit-TGIS Serving<br/>8080/HTTP + 8085/gRPC
    participant TGIS as TGIS Backend<br/>8033/gRPC (localhost)
    participant Guardrails as FMS Guardrails Orch<br/>8033/HTTP
    participant Detectors as Guardrails Detectors<br/>8080/HTTP
    participant Istio as Istio mTLS

    Note over User,Detectors: Flow 1: Inference Request with Guardrails

    User->>Envoy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443
    Envoy->>AIGateway: ext_proc (gRPC/9004)<br/>API key injection + model routing
    AIGateway-->>Envoy: Modified request + provider auth
    Envoy->>Guardrails: Forward to orchestrator<br/>HTTP/8033
    Guardrails->>Detectors: Content screening<br/>HTTP/8080 POST /api/v1/text/contents
    Detectors-->>Guardrails: Detection results
    Guardrails->>CaikitTGIS: Generation request<br/>gRPC (Caikit NLP client)
    CaikitTGIS->>TGIS: Internal forward<br/>gRPC/8033 localhost
    TGIS-->>CaikitTGIS: Generated text
    CaikitTGIS-->>Guardrails: Response
    Guardrails->>Detectors: Output screening<br/>HTTP/8080
    Detectors-->>Guardrails: Validated output
    Guardrails-->>User: Safe response

    Note over User,Detectors: Flow 2: ML Pipeline Execution

    participant CFSDK as CodeFlare SDK
    participant CFOp as CodeFlare Operator<br/>9443/HTTPS
    participant Ray as RayCluster
    participant DSP as DS Pipelines API<br/>8888/HTTP + 8887/gRPC
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB/MySQL
    participant S3 as S3/Minio

    User->>CFSDK: Submit training job<br/>Python SDK
    CFSDK->>CFOp: Create AppWrapper CR<br/>K8s API
    CFOp->>Ray: Provision RayCluster<br/>+ OAuth proxy sidecar
    Ray-->>CFSDK: Cluster ready

    User->>DSP: Create pipeline run<br/>POST /apis/v2beta1/runs
    DSP->>MariaDB: Persist run metadata<br/>SQL
    DSP->>Argo: Create Workflow CR
    Argo->>S3: Store artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443
    Argo-->>DSP: Workflow status update
    DSP-->>User: Run status

    Note over User,Detectors: Flow 3: Feature Serving (Feast)

    participant FeastOp as Feast Operator
    participant FeastSrv as Feature Server<br/>6566/HTTP
    participant OnlineStore as Online Store<br/>(Redis/PostgreSQL/etc.)

    User->>FeastSrv: POST /get-online-features<br/>HTTP/6566
    FeastSrv->>OnlineStore: Fetch feature values
    OnlineStore-->>FeastSrv: Feature vectors
    FeastSrv-->>User: Feature response

    Note over User,Detectors: Flow 4: Batch Inference

    participant BatchGW as Batch Gateway<br/>HTTP REST
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL
    participant Redis as Redis/Valkey
    participant InfGW as Inference Gateway

    User->>BatchGW: POST /v1/batches<br/>OpenAI Batch API
    BatchGW->>PostgreSQL: Persist batch job
    BatchGW->>S3: Upload input file
    BatchGW->>Redis: Enqueue processing
    BatchGW->>InfGW: Forward inference requests
    InfGW-->>BatchGW: Inference results
    BatchGW->>S3: Store output file
    BatchGW-->>User: GET /v1/batches/{id}<br/>Batch status + results
